719974f-a.title: Manhattan: Washington Street - Gansevoort Street
719974f-a.text:
Gansevoort Market Stand and Washington Street, east side, from
Gansevoort to Little West 12th Streets.
April 2, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCCIONS.

719973f-a.title: Manhattan: Gansevoort Street - Washington Street
719973f-a.text:
Gansevoort Market Stand and Gansevoort Street, south side, from
Washington Street towards West Street. The Gansevoort Pumping
Station is shown in the right background, directly in line between
the observer and Pier 52, North River.
July 9, 1932.
L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
